  "body": "### Description\n\nI understand that due to https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/23670 the default working directory for jib has changed from /work/ to /home/jboss.\r\n\r\nMounting configmaps in /work/config/application.yaml (when running the built container in k8s) no longer works, I've had to change the path to /home/jboss/config/application.yaml.\r\n\r\nIs there a way to configure the working directory?\r\n\r\nAlso maybe a note could be added to the migration guide https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-2.7 ?\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
